  3. Options hedging simulations
  4. Automated report exporting to Excel → client presentations
  5. Custom formatted order sheets for execution desk
  6. Direct access to Bob Spear for questions
- **Order Manager**: multi-account order management for CTAs; custom order
  and position reporting; full batch automation; account-level error detection;
